.DT
add_start
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
add_start

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
add_start -  This method will add a new start location to the player.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void add_start(string start_file,
string start_desc)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^start_file%^RESET%^ - the file name of the start location
%^BOLD%^start_desc%^RESET%^ - the description of the start location
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/global/player/start_position.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method will add a new start location to the player.  The
description will be used in the starts command.
.EP

.SH Example 1
.SI 5
// NB: This should be done with a define :)
player->add_start("/d/am/am/mendeddrum", "the mended drum");

.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
query_start_pos(), reset_starts(), remove_start(), query_starts(), set_start_location()
.EP

